## Funnel Strategy Workflow

Design a full-funnel media strategy:

- [ ] 1. **Journey mapping**: Map the customer journey for {{target_audience}} from awareness to retention
- [ ] 2. **Funnel stage definition**: Define what success looks like at each stage (awareness, consideration, intent, conversion, retention)
- [ ] 3. **Channel mapping**: Assign channels to funnel stages based on their natural strengths
- [ ] 4. **Message strategy**: Define messaging themes per stage (educate > inspire > convince > convert > retain)
- [ ] 5. **Audience signals**: Identify behavioral signals that indicate stage progression
- [ ] 6. **Budget weighting**: Allocate budget across funnel stages based on {{campaign_objective}}
- [ ] 7. **Retargeting flows**: Design sequential messaging and retargeting between stages
- [ ] 8. **Attribution alignment**: Map attribution model to funnel stages

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Campaign objective: {{campaign_objective}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Channels: {{channels}}
